Hideout Golf Club offers a few types of memberships which can be tailored to meet your needs. Our memberships are family memberships. We have both, refundable and non-refundable memberships. We are a club that depends on our membership to recommend interested parties for membership. For more information on becoming a member of Hideout Golf Club please contact our membership office at 239-352-4141 or fill out and submit the Membership Interest Form

ABOUT THE CLUB
Play
Dining
Pro Shop
Hideout Golf Club was established in January 2000.
The golf course, designed by renowned architect Kelly Blake Moran, was built with the purpose of providing a course that was challenging to a scratch golfer, yet enjoyable and playable for the high-handicapper. This mission was accomplished.
The "no tee-times" approach along with the ability to walk this beautiful course has resulted in a club that is the "club of choice" for the serious golfer.
The clubhouse has the charm of a rustic getaway, where epicurian dishes are prepared for you on a daily basis. Comfortable surroundings ensure an enjoyable end to your golfing day.
